docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Dec. 20--The Food and Drug Administration ended today a six-month moratorium on prescription by physicians of a widely used contraceptive device called the Dalkon Shield.

headline.main: Moratorium Is Ended by F.D.A. On IUD Challenged Over Safety
